title: Inject Text in game using LUA from the memory to run LUA in modable game (Like Wow)
description: In this video , I show how you can write some text in a third party application and send it to any LUA game by writing on the memory of specific addresses. My aim it so control the game from VR headset. Don't use it for evil or cheating purpose.
author: Éloi Strée, ꬲ🧰: Raw video
